This is by far the best cheesecake recipe that I've ever made/had. It's creamy, sweet and delicious. If you're not a fan of berries--improvise! Pour chocolate ganache over it, or swirl dulce de leche in the sour cream top...anyway you decide to top it, you won't be disappointed!

