Rating: 2
This turned out very wet and mushy, but I do not believe it was a fault in the recipe: I have recently read that cream cheese in the US contains different preservatives and stabilisers from that sold in the UK - considering I even added some cornflour to the recipe and still it was wet makes me sure it is the ingredients to blame! The flavour was good tho' - not too sweet - and the leftovers did not have to languish long in the fridge!

